description: This file serves as the entry point for the React-based frontend of the Tic Tac Toe project. It imports necessary libraries and components, sets up the root DOM node, and renders the main <App /> component within React's StrictMode.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering React components into the DOM.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders a React element into the React root.
